   Antibiotics/Vaccinations for Anthrax Exposure

    Treatment Options for Postal and Other Workers Exposed to Anthrax
     For postal and other workers. Reviews options for people exposed to
     airborne anthrax spores, who may be at risk for inhalational anthrax.
     Archived webcast provided by University of North Carolina School of
     Public Health, plus online presentation.
